1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,800
Do not buy a house

2
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:05,200
until you check

3
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:08,500
behind the mirror.

4
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:11,200
I just found out

5
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:14,000
I'm not alone here.

6
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:16,500
I pulled back

7
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:20,000
the master bedroom glass.

8
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:22,500
Behind it sat a

9
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:26,000
hidden cabinet of Polaroids.

10
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,500
Each photo shows

11
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:31,000
the same man.

12
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:34,000
He never ages.

13
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:37,000
The final photo shows

14
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:40,000
him holding an iPhone.

15
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,000
The screen light is

16
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:45,500
blindingly bright.

17
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:47,900
This room was never built.